{"tid":1039194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[財政預算案]一張圖睇嗮你得到咩福利","createTime":"2019-02-27T09:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T23:10:37.000Z","uid":123920,"like":871,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"f3560e41b6927596188c2b555cd4d15e16f6043e","tid":1039194,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gvv87XF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvv87XF.jpg&h=9e5275b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f98b77c31271e1ca065dd1c49016933d5c219a9","tid":1039194,"uid":130695,"like":403,"dislike":6,"score":397,"quote":{"pid":"f3560e41b6927596188c2b555cd4d15e16f6043e","tid":1039194,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gvv87XF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvv87XF.jpg&h=9e5275b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"香港民生 香港人福利？ 笑話<br />\n有義務無權利無享受<br />\n俾班支那畜生落黎無貢獻R著數<br />\n各種走狗賣港賊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸閪文化 偷呃擄騙搶<br />\n口技世界第一 東莞三十六式<br />\n問做雞 誰與爭峰<br />\n論外交 有睇周星馳都知啦 嘴炮呀！<br />\n屋企煮飯引致霧霾 仲可以防激光<br />\n有毒氣體對人體無害<br />\n除左騙子咩都假<br />\n紙皮豬肉包，頭髮豉油，地溝油，黑心蛋，豬瘟腸<br />\n知唔知點解有大頭奶粉呀！<br />\n因為大陸閪普遍智商低下<br />\n而腦一般同頭既呎吋成正比<br />\n點知食完都係朦撚一堆！<br />\n仲要有班傻閪唔識欣賞<br />\n你估呢啲国家特產邊度都食到咩<br />\n走黎食人地既奶 啪人地既針 拆人家庭搶人屋企<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n渣住本垃圾国護照就屌人要人認中国人<br />\n又要仆住搶其他國家護照<br />\n死磨爛磨 面皮無限厚 到班畜生拎到<br />\n即時又扮愛国 話做中国狗最好<br />\n要其他人繼續做隻中国狗要愛国<br />\n所以話中国支那賤畜蝗蟲真係幾撚恐怖<br />\n無人格無人性唯利是圖<br />\n玩個人崇拜 當個小熊維尼係皇帝<br />\n做哂太監宮女爭住奶<br />\n丫，我唔記得左<br />\n中国係最無骨氣既地方，打亂種<br />\n滿漢明清乜撚族都有<br />\n不過呢 都係中国狗，何必分那麼細<br />\n<br />\n一句 中国又贏呀！"},{"pid":"febec1fb9bea98d78e318ac0b26548c69dbdc889","tid":1039194,"uid":3189,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"乜撚都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489ef8271c8d35e839a42d48d44b6ce38d99aaf2","tid":1039194,"uid":13257,"like":168,"dislike":2,"score":166,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"屋企拎綜援嘅學生，係咪會又有$2500，又有雙糧"},{"pid":"0a959383aa9d916cc87db0bb5c7b8d6c20479389","tid":1039194,"uid":123920,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"489ef8271c8d35e839a42d48d44b6ce38d99aaf2","tid":1039194,"uid":13257,"like":168,"dislike":2,"score":166,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"屋企拎綜援嘅學生，係咪會又有$2500，又有雙糧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:11:56.000Z","msg":"應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cca651870cb404eea89efe639880cb391577678","tid":1039194,"uid":42304,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:11:59.000Z","msg":"得退稅 ，派番6000蚊先啦"},{"pid":"266f08f86fc5939a8eb44fcc6801ecab16f9763b","tid":1039194,"uid":7439,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/2-21-2018/g4f57x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F2-21-2018%2Fg4f57x.gif&h=698a0e1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6baa028e7d5cb00431a8ccd5dc26f18392b8e1d7","tid":1039194,"uid":98386,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:15:02.000Z","msg":"家住私樓免差餉 其他唔關我事"},{"pid":"edf50d29618c82df5f904216b586789a9e15f2a4","tid":1039194,"uid":19990,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"我有雙糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5495fa99d8fca7813bfb0e7ebb710a252917b47c","tid":1039194,